<div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true" style="counter-reset:line-number 0"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>这里就用到了我们上面的结论声明提升了，赋值还留着原地。</p>
<h2 id="函数声明提升" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#函数声明提升"><span>函数声明提升</span></a></h2>
